/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-02.md:55:The attacker is right that dynamic plausibility should constrain observable design much earlier. In this area, propagation is often the bottleneck. Observables with no credible transport or persistence story should be downgraded before the chain invests heavily in static estimates.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-02.md:61:Demanding an explicit transport identity or coercive persistence mechanism is appropriate as a high bar for a final positive route. But the attacker is right that using that bar as a blanket veto can misclassify informative partial mechanisms as failures. The refined chain should use persistence as an early screening and ranking device, with a stricter bar only at the final promotion stage.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-02.md:63:### 10. Step 4 lacks a concrete singular-scenario class
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-02.md:67:This criticism is correct. Persistence cannot be tested in the abstract. The refined chain should force the analyst to choose a scenario class, for example filament concentration or sheet/pancake concentration, before drawing conclusions about what can propagate.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-02.md:79:The chain is intentionally obstruction-first, and that is not itself a flaw. But the accumulation of early kill conditions, undefined terms, and decomposition freedom does create a procedural bias toward a polished negative memo. The refined chain should keep the obstruction discipline while delaying terminal judgments until the observables, scenario, and stretching representation are fixed.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-02.md:85:This is a real issue. Because the chain sits directly in an area with substantial prior work, it needs explicit calibration against Constantin-Fefferman-Majda, later vorticity-direction coherence work, and related geometric depletion or near-Beltrami discussions before claiming novelty or NS-specificity.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-02.md:91:- the chain must test control of the full stretching mechanism rather than a local geometric proxy alone;
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-02.md:101:- define localization, thresholds, and scenario classes before comparing observables;
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-02.md:103:- fix a kernel-level stretching representation before speaking of a nonlocal remainder;
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/refined/chain-02.md:5:NS-specific vortex geometry is still worth testing, but only under a protocol that prevents premature defeat. The right question is not whether a vague geometric feature "looks helpful." It is whether a sharply defined local or hybrid geometric observable, attached to a fixed localization protocol and scenario class, can control the full stretching mechanism `S omega . omega` in a way that is both scale-credible and dynamically plausible under Navier-Stokes.
