/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/refined/chain-02.md:98:  - control of the full stretching mechanism in the chosen representation,
